# Sandcastle spike: per-repo sandbox scaffold/scratch (Dockerfile, .env, logs,
# worktrees) created by `sandcastle init` at the repo root. Spike-local; never
# commit (the .env there holds the OpenAI key).
.sandcastle/
.next/
.turbo/
dist/
build/
out/
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
!.env.example
.DS_Store
# macOS Finder/iCloud Drive copy-on-conflict artifacts.
# Pattern: any path like "watcher 2.py" or "Dockerfile 3" — Finder/iCloud
# appends " N" (with leading space) before any extension when it detects a
# sibling already at the same path. Purely a sync-collision artifact, never
# source. Globs cover both with-extension (* 2.*) and bare (* 2) cases.
* [234].*
* [234]
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.log
coverage/
.nyc_output/
*.tsbuildinfo

